snippet.title: Car Garage Adventure with Roma and Oliver
snippet.description:
Roma and Oliver repaint their cars to match the color of the garages.
This is a video will spark imagination and creativity while teaching them about colors and matching. Don't miss out on this exciting Car Garage adventure!

00:00 Car Garage Adventure
03:16 Adventure behind colored doors
06:16 Kindergarten story
11:12 Learning to Count to 10
